data.message: Explore comfy-api-service project: AI image generation platform with ComfyUI backend. Two products: API (production ready, $0.01-0.05/image) and Creator SaaS (MVP in progress, $29/mo). Stack: FastAPI + ARQ + Redis + MinIO + PostgreSQL + RunPod GPU.
data.outcome: AI image generation platform with ComfyUI backend. Two products: API (production ready, $0.01-0.05/image) and Creator SaaS (MVP in progress, $29/mo). Stack: FastAPI + ARQ + Redis + MinIO + PostgreSQL + RunPod GPU.
